title: #92Noon! 10a Hour 9/19 - Ben Leber, PJ Fleck
description: Ben Leber calls in from Philadelphia to break down tonight's Vikings/Eagles game & Gophers football head coach PJ Fleck joins the show to discuss the Gophers win over Colorado, Chris Autman-Bell's injury, & more!
